  <div class="btn:save">Class = "btn:save" â†’ escaped with <code>.btn\:save</code></div>
  <div class="hash#tag">Class = "hash#tag" â†’ escaped with <code>.hash\#tag</code></div>
  <div class="100">Class = "100" â†’ escaped with <code>.\31 00</code></div>

  <p class="copyright">Copyright served </p>
